Reasoning: The paper deals with the performance of FDD massive MIMO systems with spatially correlated channels, considering the CSIT acquisition dimensionality loss, the imperfection of CSIT and the regularized-zero-forcing linear precoder. This involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), communication systems (cs.COMM), signal processing (cs.SI), networked systems (cs.NI), and multimedia (cs.MM).
